other_tests.findings: The uterus is anteverted and measures 7.9 x 4.9 x 4.5 cm. The endometrium is homogenous and measures 0.9 cm. The left ovary is within normal limits. The right ovary demonstrates multiple thick-walled anechoic cysts, with the appearance of follicles, and measures in total 6.3 x 3.1 x 4.0 cm. There is normal vascular flow within both ovaries. There is a trace amount of free fluid.
